    "founder_message_Y8wktr": {
      "type": "FounderMessage",
      "settings": {
        "founder_image": "shopify://shop_images/image_3.jpg",
        "founder_name": "Hazel Guo",
        "founder_message": "<p>YOÉ & CO. was born out of a deeply personal necessity and a desire to redefine beauty through the lens of science and ethics. The name \"Yoé\" draws inspiration from the Japanese word for \"good\", encapsulating our mission to create products that are beneficial in every sense.</p><p>In my early 20s, I faced an overwhelming health crisis. Diagnosed with a painful autoimmune disorder, I embarked on a relentless pursuit of healing through nutrition, lifestyle changes, and mindfulness. While I managed to bring most of my symptoms under control, my skin remained volatile and reactive. As a lover of luxury beauty products, the products I once adored were no longer suitable, and organic brands often fell short of the performance, sensory experience and elegance I craved.</p><p>This personal struggle inspired the creation of Yoé, a brand built on innovative biotechnology and clean, conscientious formulations. With the expertise of cosmetic scientist Luisa Fanzani, I created YOÉ & CO. , a line of clinical and dermatologist-tested, hypoallergenic skincare products suitable for even the most sensitive skin.</p><p>Our hero products, the Ympossible Creams, represent our commitment to clean beauty. They are meticulously crafted, and I am proud to say they are EWG Verified, vegan, fragrance-free, and Leaping Bunny certified.</p>",
        "founder_message_02": "<p>At Yoé, we adhere to the highest standards, formulating without gluten, parabens, phthalates, petroleum, and over 3000 harmful substances. We go beyond industry expectations, leveraging pharmaceutical-grade advanced microencapsulation biotechnology to deliver botanicals and bioengineered actives designed for controlled release and targeted delivery, ensuring your skin gets what it needs, when it needs it.</p><p>Our philosophy is rooted in science-backed, clean formulations using biotech ingredients, high-design packaging, and sustainability initiatives.</p>",
        "signature": "Founder, YOÉ & CO."
      }
    }
